%!PS-Adobe-2.0 EPSF-2.0
%%Title: wurz.eps
%%Creator: Cinderella Version 1.0
%%Port: de.cinderella.ports.EuclideanPort
%%CreationDate: Apr 6, 2005 9:49:42 PM
